               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡; Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡; Absolution of the Son, ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡; For the sake of peaceful holy things, በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡; Anaphora of Our Lord, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡; God of the Luminaries, እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="14v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT2260salota"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="14v" to="25v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT2444Temher"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ትምሕርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡ ቅድመ፡ ዘትትነገር፡ እምጵርስፎራ፡...</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="25v" to="30r"/>
